1
00:00:24,030 --> 00:00:25,290
[Adapted from a novel published on
Qidian Reading under China Literature]

2
00:00:25,320 --> 00:00:27,180
["Way of Choices" by Mao Ni]

3
00:00:28,300 --> 00:00:29,830
[Minors]

4
00:00:29,860 --> 00:00:31,550
[should watch with guardian consent]

5
00:02:14,400 --> 00:02:19,480
[Way of Choices]

6
00:02:21,170 --> 00:02:22,360
The North-South Alliance

7
00:02:21,230 --> 00:02:24,850
[Previously]

8
00:02:22,360 --> 00:02:23,880
is vital to the future of the Human Race.

9
00:02:23,880 --> 00:02:25,320
If you were smart enough,

10
00:02:25,480 --> 00:02:27,280
you wouldn't have shown up tonight.

11
00:02:27,280 --> 00:02:30,280
If my daughter's marriage
can benefit the Human Race,

12
00:02:27,430 --> 00:02:28,340
[Betrothal Contract]
[Witness: Prince Chen Liu]

13
00:02:30,280 --> 00:02:32,010
it's an honor for the Xu family.

14
00:02:32,280 --> 00:02:33,240
Why

15
00:02:33,440 --> 00:02:35,300
is everyone guarding against me?

16
00:02:35,480 --> 00:02:36,560
I'm afraid Chen Changsheng

17
00:02:35,770 --> 00:02:36,450
[Tong Palace Formation]

18
00:02:36,560 --> 00:02:38,640
won't make it for the banquet.

19
00:02:38,960 --> 00:02:40,760
No matter what trap you have set,

20
00:02:40,840 --> 00:02:42,240
Master will break it!

21
00:02:42,400 --> 00:02:43,329
It's the palace.

22
00:02:43,680 --> 00:02:44,440
I'm out!

23
00:02:45,079 --> 00:02:46,800
What a good kid.

24
00:02:47,120 --> 00:02:48,280
It'd be even better

25
00:02:48,440 --> 00:02:50,040
if his last name was not Chen.

26
00:02:50,200 --> 00:02:53,400
Is there anyone against the marriage between Qiushan Jun

27
00:02:53,680 --> 00:02:54,840
and Xu Yourong?

28
00:02:55,880 --> 00:02:57,079
I object.

29
00:03:05,800 --> 00:03:06,680
I object!

30
00:03:13,680 --> 00:03:14,920
Someone's actually objecting?

31
00:03:14,920 --> 00:03:16,000
Who is he?

32
00:03:16,000 --> 00:03:17,560
What right does he have to oppose it?

33
00:03:17,560 --> 00:03:18,760
Is he courting death?

34
00:03:23,470 --> 00:03:25,700
Who are you, bastard?

35
00:03:25,880 --> 00:03:27,760
How dare you make noise in the palace!

36
00:03:27,760 --> 00:03:28,440
Guards!

37
00:03:28,840 --> 00:03:30,280
Drag this man out.

38
00:03:36,640 --> 00:03:38,320
I don't care who you are

39
00:03:38,340 --> 00:03:39,600
or where you come from.

40
00:03:39,640 --> 00:03:41,800
I am here to arrest an imperial fugitive.

41
00:03:41,800 --> 00:03:43,480
Who dares stop me?

42
00:03:43,680 --> 00:03:45,000
Imperial fugitive?

43
00:03:45,320 --> 00:03:47,280
What imperial fugitive?

44
00:03:48,040 --> 00:03:49,720
This kid

45
00:03:49,720 --> 00:03:52,520
is the director
of the State Religious Academy.

46
00:03:52,880 --> 00:03:54,760
Even if he's late,

47
00:03:54,880 --> 00:03:57,810
that doesn't make him
an imperial fugitive, does it?

48
00:04:00,360 --> 00:04:02,360
But he spoke against this marriage.

49
00:04:03,600 --> 00:04:06,760
Since the ceremony includes
asking whether anyone objects,

50
00:04:06,760 --> 00:04:10,360
naturally, there should
be room for someone to oppose.

51
00:04:13,760 --> 00:04:14,620
Your Highness.

52
00:04:14,840 --> 00:04:16,560
What is going on?

53
00:04:17,600 --> 00:04:18,600
Well...

54
00:04:19,000 --> 00:04:20,120
Outside the hall,

55
00:04:20,240 --> 00:04:21,399
I heard Your Highness ask

56
00:04:21,399 --> 00:04:23,720
if anyone was against the marriage between Qiushan Jun

57
00:04:23,720 --> 00:04:24,680
and Xu Yourong.

58
00:04:25,080 --> 00:04:26,340
Miss Xu is not present.

59
00:04:26,400 --> 00:04:28,160
This is a marriage based on interests.

60
00:04:28,160 --> 00:04:29,760
I think she would not like it.

61
00:04:30,160 --> 00:04:31,160
So I said

62
00:04:31,280 --> 00:04:32,040
I object.

63
00:04:32,720 --> 00:04:34,240
What right do you have to object?

64
00:04:34,240 --> 00:04:35,880
This is between the Lishan Sword Sect

65
00:04:35,880 --> 00:04:37,159
and the Divine General's Estate.

66
00:04:37,159 --> 00:04:38,560
What has it to do with you?

67
00:04:38,920 --> 00:04:41,250
Xu Yourong and I have a marriage contract.

68
00:04:42,440 --> 00:04:43,800
She is my fiancée.

69
00:04:43,960 --> 00:04:46,159
Of course she can't marry someone else.

70
00:04:48,920 --> 00:04:49,920
Ridiculous!

71
00:04:49,920 --> 00:04:52,920
I've never heard of Yourong
having a marriage contract.

72
00:04:52,920 --> 00:04:54,360
You shameless fool,

73
00:04:54,400 --> 00:04:55,560
how dare you humiliate Lishan?

74
00:04:55,560 --> 00:04:56,440
Who would believe that?

75
00:04:56,440 --> 00:04:59,080
-The Saintess would never marry a loser.
-You said you have a marriage contract.

76
00:04:59,080 --> 00:05:00,340
What proof do you have?

77
00:05:01,160 --> 00:05:02,890
I have the betrothal contract.

78
00:05:04,570 --> 00:05:08,110
[Betrothal Contract]

79
00:05:06,760 --> 00:05:07,440
This is...

80
00:05:08,240 --> 00:05:09,900
the seal of the Grand Pontiff.

81
00:05:11,480 --> 00:05:12,480
This betrothal contract is real?

82
00:05:12,480 --> 00:05:13,800
Divine General of the East?

83
00:05:13,800 --> 00:05:14,680
What's going on?

84
00:05:14,680 --> 00:05:16,040
Bastard!

85
00:05:16,840 --> 00:05:18,520
Since the betrothal contract is real,

86
00:05:18,520 --> 00:05:21,000
it means someone is trying
to deceive everyone

87
00:05:21,000 --> 00:05:23,130
and sell his daughter for a good price.

88
00:05:23,920 --> 00:05:25,720
As expected of a divine general.

89
00:05:25,720 --> 00:05:27,000
You're great at war

90
00:05:27,000 --> 00:05:28,200
and also at business.

91
00:05:30,640 --> 00:05:31,320
Senior.

92
00:05:33,920 --> 00:05:35,960
People say marriage is the parents' choice

93
00:05:35,960 --> 00:05:37,130
and the matchmaker's arrangement.

94
00:05:37,130 --> 00:05:40,730
[Gou Hanshi, Lishan Sword Sect]

95
00:05:37,520 --> 00:05:39,380
We've got the first part covered.

96
00:05:39,440 --> 00:05:41,360
With the betrothal contract in your hands,

97
00:05:41,360 --> 00:05:42,890
you've got the second part.

98
00:05:43,320 --> 00:05:43,880
But

99
00:05:44,320 --> 00:05:45,560
these are not important.

100
00:05:45,560 --> 00:05:46,600
What matters is

101
00:05:47,000 --> 00:05:48,800
whom Junior Xu wishes to marry.

102
00:05:50,320 --> 00:05:53,690
[Guan Feibai, Lishan Sword Sect]

103
00:05:51,480 --> 00:05:52,760
Everyone knows

104
00:05:52,810 --> 00:05:55,680
Junior Xu and Senior Qiushan Jun
have been childhood sweethearts

105
00:05:55,680 --> 00:05:57,140
with an unbreakable bond.

106
00:05:57,320 --> 00:05:59,200
Even if your betrothal contract is real,

107
00:05:59,200 --> 00:06:01,730
does that mean Junior Sister
has to marry you?

108
00:06:03,960 --> 00:06:05,890
If you really care about Junior Xu,

109
00:06:06,120 --> 00:06:08,360
shouldn't you respect her wishes?

110
00:06:14,080 --> 00:06:16,340
Isn't this Junior Sister's white crane?

111
00:06:16,400 --> 00:06:17,960
It's Yourong's white crane!

112
00:06:17,960 --> 00:06:21,160
Junior Sister sent the sacred beast
to accept Qiushan's marriage contract.

113
00:06:21,160 --> 00:06:22,530
That says it all.

114
00:06:34,080 --> 00:06:35,040
Long time no see.

115
00:07:00,840 --> 00:07:03,570
Thank you all for your concern
about my marriage.

116
00:07:03,600 --> 00:07:04,840
But I didn't know

117
00:07:05,320 --> 00:07:06,480
about the proposal.

118
00:07:06,960 --> 00:07:07,640
So,

119
00:07:07,680 --> 00:07:08,680
I don't like it.

120
00:07:09,830 --> 00:07:11,040
Father, Mother.

121
00:07:11,640 --> 00:07:13,040
Senior Qiushan is great.

122
00:07:13,110 --> 00:07:14,190
I respect him.

123
00:07:14,750 --> 00:07:16,350
But I don't want to marry him,

124
00:07:16,840 --> 00:07:17,560
because

125
00:07:18,480 --> 00:07:20,230
I already have a marriage contract.

126
00:07:20,230 --> 00:07:21,300
[Betrothal Contract]

127
00:07:22,070 --> 00:07:23,630
My fiance is called

128
00:07:25,120 --> 00:07:26,680
Chen Changsheng.

129
00:08:15,200 --> 00:08:16,480
As expected of Xu Yourong.

130
00:08:16,480 --> 00:08:17,040
So cool!

131
00:08:17,040 --> 00:08:18,480
Childhood sweethearts?

132
00:08:18,480 --> 00:08:19,920
Unbreakable bond?

133
00:08:21,600 --> 00:08:23,920
More like wishful thinking.

134
00:08:23,920 --> 00:08:24,720
How insolent!

135
00:08:25,000 --> 00:08:27,410
Xu Yourong is
the Heavenly Phoenix Saintess.

136
00:08:27,410 --> 00:08:29,720
Qiushan Jun is the True Dragon incarnate!

137
00:08:29,720 --> 00:08:31,640
The North-South Alliance
is of great importance!

138
00:08:31,640 --> 00:08:33,090
In order to resist the Demon Race,

139
00:08:33,090 --> 00:08:34,650
what is a small

140
00:08:34,679 --> 00:08:35,720
personal sacrifice?

141
00:08:35,720 --> 00:08:36,440
Exactly!

142
00:08:36,440 --> 00:08:37,960
The North-South Alliance
is the Human Race's greater cause.

143
00:08:37,960 --> 00:08:39,679
It is the Saintess' duty
to marry for alliance!

144
00:08:39,679 --> 00:08:41,760
This loser wants the Saintess to himself.

145
00:08:41,760 --> 00:08:42,960
How selfish!

146
00:08:43,080 --> 00:08:45,080
Humans truly are shameless.

147
00:08:45,320 --> 00:08:46,600
Have you no shame?

148
00:08:47,000 --> 00:08:48,000
No need

149
00:08:48,040 --> 00:08:49,160
to argue with these people.

150
00:08:49,160 --> 00:08:50,370
No, no, no.

151
00:08:50,520 --> 00:08:51,920
When it comes to insults,

152
00:08:51,950 --> 00:08:53,210
we can't lose.

153
00:08:53,720 --> 00:08:54,480
But...

154
00:08:54,800 --> 00:08:56,320
I'm not good at this.

155
00:08:56,960 --> 00:08:57,760
Want to learn?

156
00:08:58,320 --> 00:08:59,180
I'll teach you.

157
00:09:00,400 --> 00:09:01,480
Insolent?

158
00:09:01,570 --> 00:09:02,940
Screw your "insolent"!

159
00:09:02,940 --> 00:09:04,270
Who do you think you are?

160
00:09:04,510 --> 00:09:07,070
How dare you deny a marriage contract
witnessed by the Grand Pontiff?

161
00:09:07,070 --> 00:09:09,000
Are you looking down on Grand Zhou?

162
00:09:09,000 --> 00:09:10,400
You...

163
00:09:10,480 --> 00:09:12,410
Resisting the Demon Race? Really?

164
00:09:12,510 --> 00:09:14,880
The Xiaosong family
has never been on the front lines!

165
00:09:12,620 --> 00:09:15,020
[The Xiaosong family
has never been on the front lines!]

166
00:09:14,880 --> 00:09:16,120
But when it comes to stirring up
North-South tensions

167
00:09:15,120 --> 00:09:17,060
[But when it comes to stirring up
North-South tensions to profit]

168
00:09:16,120 --> 00:09:17,150
to profit,

169
00:09:17,320 --> 00:09:19,250
you're more diligent than anyone!

170
00:09:19,440 --> 00:09:21,120
You little thing!

171
00:09:21,190 --> 00:09:22,360
You old thing!

172
00:09:23,790 --> 00:09:24,990
All you talk about is this great cause,

173
00:09:24,990 --> 00:09:26,230
yet you betray humanity.

174
00:09:26,230 --> 00:09:27,500
Shameless, brazen

175
00:09:27,860 --> 00:09:29,320
and utterly disgraceful!

176
00:09:32,720 --> 00:09:35,040
How dare you three little brats

177
00:09:35,120 --> 00:09:36,760
speak rudely?

178
00:09:37,040 --> 00:09:37,840
Today,

179
00:09:37,840 --> 00:09:40,120
I'll teach you a lesson
on behalf of your folks!

180
00:09:40,120 --> 00:09:40,840
-No.
-Stop!

181
00:09:48,160 --> 00:09:50,220
When dealing with shameless people,

182
00:09:50,440 --> 00:09:51,960
you have to

183
00:09:51,960 --> 00:09:53,220
slap their faces hard.

184
00:09:59,440 --> 00:10:01,000
J-J-Jin Yulyu?

185
00:10:01,200 --> 00:10:02,560
Why are you here?

186
00:10:02,560 --> 00:10:03,560
Jin Yulyu?

187
00:10:03,720 --> 00:10:05,400
Leader of the Four Great Yao Generals?

188
00:10:05,400 --> 00:10:07,320
Wasn't he serving
the Yao Emperor in Baidi City?

189
00:10:07,320 --> 00:10:08,760
What is happening today?

190
00:10:10,360 --> 00:10:12,040
If Jin Yulyu is here,

191
00:10:12,040 --> 00:10:13,400
then that girl...

192
00:10:13,400 --> 00:10:14,120
Master,

193
00:10:14,440 --> 00:10:16,520
I didn't mean to hide my identity.

194
00:10:17,760 --> 00:10:18,920
Leave the rest to me.

195
00:10:20,520 --> 00:10:21,560
My surname is Bai.

196
00:10:21,920 --> 00:10:23,250
Bai as in Emperor Baidi.

197
00:10:26,920 --> 00:10:27,840
My mother

198
00:10:28,680 --> 00:10:30,840
is the Grand Princess of West Continent.

199
00:10:30,460 --> 00:10:33,460
[Bai Luoheng, Yao Princess]

200
00:10:33,360 --> 00:10:34,280
My father

201
00:10:35,000 --> 00:10:36,440
is Bai Xingye.

202
00:10:35,250 --> 00:10:36,990
[800 Li Red River]

203
00:10:51,680 --> 00:10:52,640
My master

204
00:10:53,080 --> 00:10:54,240
is Chen Changsheng.

205
00:11:04,590 --> 00:11:06,040
Speaking of the greater cause,

206
00:11:06,040 --> 00:11:07,160
don't forget, when

207
00:11:07,440 --> 00:11:09,880
Emperor Taizong led the northern campaign
against the Demon Race

208
00:11:09,880 --> 00:11:11,410
and won a decisive victory,

209
00:11:11,720 --> 00:11:14,520
it was the Yao
who fought alongside the Human Race.

210
00:11:14,960 --> 00:11:18,040
1.8 million young warriors
shed their blood in the northern lands.

211
00:11:18,040 --> 00:11:20,280
The Human Race and the Yao
fought side by side,

212
00:11:20,280 --> 00:11:21,560
forging an eternal alliance

213
00:11:21,560 --> 00:11:23,160
to govern the world in unity.

214
00:11:23,600 --> 00:11:24,530
The great cause?

215
00:11:24,960 --> 00:11:26,610
I am the true greater cause!

216
00:11:27,080 --> 00:11:29,320
And you use this greater cause
to threaten my master?

217
00:11:29,320 --> 00:11:30,450
How ridiculous!

218
00:11:30,560 --> 00:11:31,320
Tell me.

219
00:11:31,560 --> 00:11:33,820
How is my master inferior to Qiushan Jun?

220
00:11:34,040 --> 00:11:35,440
For the North-South Alliance,

221
00:11:35,440 --> 00:11:37,800
Xu Yourong must marry Qiushan Jun?

222
00:11:38,080 --> 00:11:39,680
Just because of
the so-called greater cause,

223
00:11:39,680 --> 00:11:42,280
a woman must wed a man
she doesn't want to marry?

224
00:11:42,640 --> 00:11:44,700
My master's wife must marry another?

225
00:11:45,080 --> 00:11:46,320
I really wonder

226
00:11:46,480 --> 00:11:48,280
if you guys are spies of the Demon Race!

227
00:11:48,280 --> 00:11:49,340
You... you guys...

228
00:11:51,000 --> 00:11:51,640
Master.

229
00:11:52,200 --> 00:11:52,880
Let's go.

230
00:11:58,720 --> 00:11:59,320
Tang Tang.

231
00:11:59,600 --> 00:12:00,660
What are you doing?

232
00:12:00,960 --> 00:12:02,880
If you return and apologize
to the seniors now,

233
00:12:02,880 --> 00:12:03,880
it's not too late.

234
00:12:04,280 --> 00:12:05,160
Apologize?

235
00:12:05,280 --> 00:12:06,120
Boring.

236
00:12:06,520 --> 00:12:07,720
Tiandao Academy is boring.

237
00:12:07,720 --> 00:12:08,520
So are you.

238
00:12:09,040 --> 00:12:09,800
So,

239
00:12:10,240 --> 00:12:11,760
I've decided to leave Tiandao Academy.

240
00:12:11,520 --> 00:12:13,470
[Tiandao Academy]

241
00:12:13,960 --> 00:12:14,360
You...

242
00:12:15,600 --> 00:12:16,660
If you drop out,

243
00:12:16,960 --> 00:12:19,160
you can't take the Imperial Court Exam!

244
00:12:20,560 --> 00:12:21,400
At the time,

245
00:12:22,000 --> 00:12:23,600
people couldn't understand

246
00:12:24,000 --> 00:12:26,480
why the youths
of the State Religious Academy

247
00:12:26,480 --> 00:12:28,280
were so reckless

248
00:12:29,320 --> 00:12:32,180
to turn this feast
that should have changed history

249
00:12:32,560 --> 00:12:34,360
into a farce.

250
00:12:34,640 --> 00:12:36,400
Students of the State Religious Academy

251
00:12:36,400 --> 00:12:38,530
may also take the Imperial Court Exam.

252
00:12:38,760 --> 00:12:39,280
Great.

253
00:12:39,600 --> 00:12:40,440
Count me in.

254
00:12:40,840 --> 00:12:41,840
Great!

255
00:12:42,080 --> 00:12:43,440
There are four of us now!

256
00:12:44,880 --> 00:12:46,200
On our way here,

257
00:12:46,200 --> 00:12:48,080
we heard that
the State Religious Academy reopened

258
00:12:48,080 --> 00:12:49,480
and wanted to have a look.

259
00:12:49,560 --> 00:12:50,400
Unfortunately,

260
00:12:50,400 --> 00:12:52,360
we missed the first night
of the Qingteng Banquet.

261
00:12:52,360 --> 00:12:53,160
Fortunately,

262
00:12:53,680 --> 00:12:56,400
today is the third night
of the Qingteng Banquet.

263
00:12:56,400 --> 00:12:57,600
The Lishan Sword Sect

264
00:12:57,800 --> 00:12:59,640
invites the State Religious Academy

265
00:12:59,640 --> 00:13:00,640
to teach us.

266
00:13:01,800 --> 00:13:03,200
High-sounding words.

267
00:13:03,720 --> 00:13:05,280
You just want revenge.

268
00:13:05,280 --> 00:13:05,920
Yes.

269
00:13:06,480 --> 00:13:07,320
As a disciple,

270
00:13:07,800 --> 00:13:09,280
I must protect my sect.

271
00:13:09,680 --> 00:13:10,680
As a junior,

272
00:13:10,980 --> 00:13:13,440
I want to show my senior's stance
on behalf of him.

273
00:13:13,440 --> 00:13:14,370
Please teach me.

274
00:13:16,960 --> 00:13:18,160
How shall we compete?

275
00:13:18,440 --> 00:13:20,360
I heard that you failed
to do Marrow Cleansing successfully

276
00:13:20,360 --> 00:13:21,480
and lack the True Essence.

277
00:13:21,480 --> 00:13:22,400
So, I think

278
00:13:22,400 --> 00:13:24,860
a civil test and a martial test
would be good.

279
00:13:25,800 --> 00:13:27,280
Each side sends two people.

280
00:13:27,280 --> 00:13:28,880
One commands, one competes.

281
00:13:29,200 --> 00:13:29,760
Okay?

282
00:13:30,080 --> 00:13:30,600
No.

283
00:13:31,000 --> 00:13:33,560
Rumor has it that this guy has read
The Three Thousand Daoist Scriptures.

284
00:13:33,560 --> 00:13:34,620
Competing with him

285
00:13:34,680 --> 00:13:35,640
is suicide!

286
00:13:36,080 --> 00:13:37,560
I think that's very interesting.

287
00:13:37,560 --> 00:13:38,680
Let's start now.

288
00:13:39,360 --> 00:13:40,600
The master bears the duty,

289
00:13:40,600 --> 00:13:42,160
and the disciple bears the effort.

290
00:13:42,160 --> 00:13:43,110
I'm new.

291
00:13:43,320 --> 00:13:44,380
Let me show myself.

292
00:13:47,280 --> 00:13:48,720
The Divine Nation's Seven Prodigies

293
00:13:48,720 --> 00:13:50,720
all rank high on the Blue Cloud List.

294
00:13:51,080 --> 00:13:52,680
Even the weakest Qi Jian

295
00:13:52,680 --> 00:13:53,520
is 11th.

296
00:13:54,400 --> 00:13:56,930
Theoretically, we have no chance
of winning.

297
00:13:57,280 --> 00:13:58,280
Do you have a plan?

298
00:13:58,720 --> 00:14:00,250
Listen to my command later.

299
00:14:01,400 --> 00:14:03,260
Now you're acting like a teacher.

300
00:14:03,360 --> 00:14:04,020
I trust you.

301
00:14:06,480 --> 00:14:07,720
Kids,

302
00:14:07,720 --> 00:14:09,520
that's enough.

303
00:14:09,640 --> 00:14:11,680
This round will decide the winner.

304
00:14:11,920 --> 00:14:13,160
Off you go!

305
00:14:14,260 --> 00:14:16,810
[Tang Thirty-Six, State Religious Academy]

306
00:14:17,090 --> 00:14:19,720
[Qingteng Banquet: State Religious Academy
versus Lishan Sword Sect]

307
00:14:20,360 --> 00:14:22,620
Tang family treasure, the Wenshui Sword

308
00:14:23,000 --> 00:14:26,080
versus Lishan Sword Sect's 1000-year-old
Iron Ruler Sword.

309
00:14:23,240 --> 00:14:25,970
[Qi Jian, Lishan Sword Sect]

310
00:14:27,040 --> 00:14:28,560
How exciting.

311
00:14:46,000 --> 00:14:47,330
Water-striking sword.

312
00:14:48,240 --> 00:14:49,770
Song Mountain clouds rise.

313
00:14:55,080 --> 00:14:55,880
So strong.

314
00:14:55,880 --> 00:14:57,680
Mountain spirits splits rocks.

315
00:15:01,200 --> 00:15:02,660
Upside-down golden vase.

316
00:15:02,760 --> 00:15:04,160
Star hook across the sky!

317
00:15:04,520 --> 00:15:05,720
Submerging sea mist.

318
00:15:05,800 --> 00:15:07,080
Dewfall on falling Wutong.

319
00:15:07,080 --> 00:15:08,480
Lantern shadow on the casement.

320
00:15:08,480 --> 00:15:09,180
Toppling the golden crow.

321
00:15:09,180 --> 00:15:11,380
Donglin Seven-Star Sword, Third Form.

322
00:15:14,680 --> 00:15:16,210
Such exquisite swordplay.

323
00:15:16,240 --> 00:15:17,480
I've never seen this before.

324
00:15:17,480 --> 00:15:19,600
It's from the Qingjiang Sect
in Donglin Prefecture.

325
00:15:19,600 --> 00:15:21,330
It's a small countryside sect.

326
00:15:21,360 --> 00:15:22,890
It's not in the Scriptures.

327
00:15:23,880 --> 00:15:25,540
Hengjiang Sword, Third Form.

328
00:15:29,440 --> 00:15:31,000
There's such a counter move?

329
00:15:31,000 --> 00:15:32,680
But the True Essence of these swords

330
00:15:32,680 --> 00:15:33,760
should not connect.

331
00:15:33,760 --> 00:15:35,040
I was frail since childhood,

332
00:15:35,040 --> 00:15:36,240
and studied medicine

333
00:15:36,280 --> 00:15:37,480
so I know a little about meridians.

334
00:15:37,480 --> 00:15:39,600
So you fused sword arts
with meridian arts.

335
00:15:39,600 --> 00:15:40,420
Impressive.

336
00:15:44,320 --> 00:15:47,400
When Zhou Dufu and Emperor Taizong fought,

337
00:15:47,400 --> 00:15:49,000
it was just so.

338
00:15:49,200 --> 00:15:50,760
Director, why do you say that?

339
00:15:50,760 --> 00:15:52,080
In terms of cultivation,

340
00:15:52,080 --> 00:15:53,590
they are far behind.

341
00:15:54,040 --> 00:15:56,160
But to merge different schools
of swordsmanship

342
00:15:56,160 --> 00:15:57,800
so exquisitely

343
00:15:58,160 --> 00:15:59,920
at their age

344
00:16:00,360 --> 00:16:01,960
is remarkable.

345
00:16:04,560 --> 00:16:05,920
Thirteen returning blades.

346
00:16:05,920 --> 00:16:07,180
I don't know this move.

347
00:16:07,480 --> 00:16:08,280
It doesn't matter.

348
00:16:08,280 --> 00:16:09,880
Use evening clouds retract.

349
00:16:12,080 --> 00:16:13,200
Hengshan Sword!

350
00:16:14,760 --> 00:16:16,020
Setting sun hangs low.

351
00:16:19,640 --> 00:16:22,240
As the evening clouds retract
and the setting sun hangs low...

352
00:16:22,240 --> 00:16:22,840
Be careful!

353
00:16:22,840 --> 00:16:24,900
then follows an autumn maple strike!

354
00:16:32,480 --> 00:16:34,400
These are the 3 strongest moves
of Wenshui Sword.

355
00:16:34,400 --> 00:16:35,600
It consumes a lot of energy.

356
00:16:35,600 --> 00:16:36,920
We'll win if we can hold defence!

357
00:16:36,920 --> 00:16:37,680
No.

358
00:16:37,680 --> 00:16:38,600
We can't defend.

359
00:16:38,600 --> 00:16:40,530
Break out with the Yuanshan Sword!

360
00:16:44,720 --> 00:16:45,320
Retreat.

361
00:16:46,400 --> 00:16:47,260
Retreat again.

362
00:16:47,400 --> 00:16:49,530
Evening song from the fisher’s shore.

363
00:16:49,760 --> 00:16:50,680
Good chance!

364
00:16:51,290 --> 00:16:52,000
Qi Jian!

365
00:16:52,160 --> 00:16:53,220
Don't be reckless.

366
00:16:53,320 --> 00:16:54,400
Lift 3 inches,

367
00:16:55,520 --> 00:16:57,580
hook the sword over the great forest!

368
00:16:58,320 --> 00:16:59,600
Hook the sword over the great forest,

369
00:16:59,600 --> 00:17:01,400
the opening form of the Kaizong Sword.

370
00:17:01,400 --> 00:17:02,330
What use is that?

371
00:17:03,360 --> 00:17:04,280
Chen Changsheng,

372
00:17:04,280 --> 00:17:05,770
I trust you!

373
00:17:18,960 --> 00:17:19,760
I lost.

374
00:17:23,480 --> 00:17:24,540
Why are you crying?

375
00:17:24,640 --> 00:17:25,839
I didn't beat you.

376
00:17:26,040 --> 00:17:27,900
The State Religious Academy did.

377
00:17:29,120 --> 00:17:31,680
The State Religious Academy

378
00:17:31,680 --> 00:17:33,480
wins.

379
00:17:43,360 --> 00:17:44,000
Senior.

380
00:17:44,400 --> 00:17:45,320
I'm sorry.

381
00:17:45,720 --> 00:17:47,320
I acted on my own.

382
00:17:48,840 --> 00:17:49,600
It's okay.

383
00:17:50,040 --> 00:17:50,970
We'll win it back

384
00:17:51,200 --> 00:17:52,730
at the Imperial Court Exam.

385
00:17:52,800 --> 00:17:53,880
A game

386
00:17:54,120 --> 00:17:55,520
doesn't prove strength.

387
00:17:55,760 --> 00:17:57,360
Dare to fight us for real?

388
00:17:57,680 --> 00:17:58,920
Best of three.

389
00:17:59,160 --> 00:17:59,840
What?

390
00:18:00,040 --> 00:18:01,720
The Lishan Sword Sect

391
00:18:01,720 --> 00:18:02,640
cannot accept defeat?

392
00:18:02,640 --> 00:18:04,800
Your Highness is only 9th
on the Blue Cloud List.

393
00:18:04,800 --> 00:18:05,920
I'm the 4th.

394
00:18:06,200 --> 00:18:07,040
4th and 9th

395
00:18:07,360 --> 00:18:08,360
are worlds apart!

396
00:18:10,680 --> 00:18:12,440
Upper realm of silent reflection.

397
00:18:12,440 --> 00:18:14,680
That's Guan Feibai's self-created
Feibai Sword Technique!

398
00:18:14,680 --> 00:18:15,810
Aren't you worried?

399
00:18:16,040 --> 00:18:18,680
He's the 4th Prodigy
of the Divine Nation's Seven Prodigies.

400
00:18:18,680 --> 00:18:20,000
If ranking alone mattered,

401
00:18:20,000 --> 00:18:21,640
why hold the Qingteng Banquet?

402
00:18:21,640 --> 00:18:23,450
What's the point
of the Imperial Court Exam?

403
00:18:23,220 --> 00:18:24,050
[Upper Realm of Silent Reflection]

404
00:18:24,360 --> 00:18:24,960
What?

405
00:18:25,360 --> 00:18:26,480
In just a few months,

406
00:18:26,480 --> 00:18:29,680
Her Highness has reached
the upper realm of silent reflection too?

407
00:18:29,680 --> 00:18:31,010
Zhongshan Storm Sword!

408
00:18:31,420 --> 00:18:32,760
Embracing the rain!

409
00:18:31,900 --> 00:18:33,170
[Embracing the Rain,
Zhongshan Storm Sword]

410
00:18:33,390 --> 00:18:34,050
What?

411
00:18:34,080 --> 00:18:35,800
How can a Yao
comprehend a human technique?

412
00:18:35,800 --> 00:18:36,480
Break!

413
00:18:40,480 --> 00:18:41,160
Suppress.

414
00:18:43,440 --> 00:18:44,300
I didn't expect

415
00:18:44,800 --> 00:18:47,040
that Hanshi is already
Approaching the Profound Truth.

416
00:18:47,040 --> 00:18:48,080
Nor did I expect

417
00:18:48,640 --> 00:18:50,440
Princess Luo to improve so fast

418
00:18:50,920 --> 00:18:52,480
and break through her bloodline limits

419
00:18:52,480 --> 00:18:54,080
under your teaching.

420
00:18:54,640 --> 00:18:55,640
Chen Changsheng.

421
00:18:55,800 --> 00:18:57,000
You deserve the title

422
00:18:57,440 --> 00:18:58,480
of director.

423
00:18:59,400 --> 00:19:00,800
I heard from the Tang Thirty-Six

424
00:19:00,800 --> 00:19:02,120
that you have read all the Scriptures

425
00:19:02,120 --> 00:19:03,360
and are remarkable.

426
00:19:03,760 --> 00:19:05,400
The only thing I can do is study hard.

427
00:19:05,400 --> 00:19:07,160
Reading is my cultivation.

428
00:19:08,600 --> 00:19:09,200
Perfect.

429
00:19:09,640 --> 00:19:10,700
I like reading too.

430
00:19:11,280 --> 00:19:13,120
I'll take the Imperial Court Exam too.

431
00:19:13,120 --> 00:19:13,720
There,

432
00:19:14,680 --> 00:19:16,740
we'll decide who's the winner again.

433
00:19:18,600 --> 00:19:19,880
He's already
Approaching the Profound Truth

434
00:19:19,880 --> 00:19:21,610
but he didn't bully with realm.

435
00:19:21,800 --> 00:19:22,760
He's a gentleman.

436
00:19:22,760 --> 00:19:23,840
What are you thinking?

437
00:19:23,840 --> 00:19:25,160
We won tonight.

438
00:19:25,280 --> 00:19:26,280
Isn't that great?

439
00:19:26,440 --> 00:19:27,400
Yes, Master.

440
00:19:27,480 --> 00:19:29,120
We must celebrate.

441
00:19:29,760 --> 00:19:31,200
I heard there was a fight!

442
00:19:32,960 --> 00:19:35,690
Who dares to insult
the State Religious Academy?

443
00:19:36,560 --> 00:19:37,420
Where are they?

444
00:19:41,480 --> 00:19:42,760
You youngsters!

445
00:19:42,920 --> 00:19:44,520
Do you know what you've done?

446
00:19:47,120 --> 00:19:48,600
You disregarded the great cause!

447
00:19:48,600 --> 00:19:49,560
Absurd!

448
00:19:49,640 --> 00:19:50,560
Insolent!

449
00:19:51,440 --> 00:19:52,240
Later,

450
00:19:52,840 --> 00:19:54,360
Tang Thirty-Six said,

451
00:19:55,280 --> 00:19:56,560
true youths

452
00:19:56,880 --> 00:19:58,600
do not rejoice at spring breeze,

453
00:19:58,600 --> 00:20:00,100
nor grieve at autumn wind,

454
00:20:00,560 --> 00:20:01,920
nor sigh at winter snow,

455
00:20:02,600 --> 00:20:04,200
nor tire of summer cicadas.

456
00:20:05,040 --> 00:20:06,770
They rejoice at what they love,

457
00:20:07,000 --> 00:20:08,660
are annoyed by what they hate,

458
00:20:08,670 --> 00:20:10,360
[Officiant: Divine General of the East,
Xu Shiji]

459
00:20:09,280 --> 00:20:11,040
are bothered by injustice,

460
00:20:10,390 --> 00:20:12,160
[Chief of Qiushan, Qiushan Yuanxin]

461
00:20:11,640 --> 00:20:13,770
and grieve only at a heroic silhouette

462
00:20:14,240 --> 00:20:15,360
under sunset.

463
00:20:15,960 --> 00:20:17,400
True in their love,

464
00:20:17,600 --> 00:20:18,560
and true

465
00:20:18,640 --> 00:20:19,960
in their scorn.

466
00:20:20,440 --> 00:20:21,320
So...

467
00:20:20,760 --> 00:20:22,790
[They Don't Care]

468
00:20:21,960 --> 00:20:23,720
they don't care.

469
00:20:22,810 --> 00:20:26,350
[The Young Director: Episode 6]

470
00:20:27,160 --> 00:20:27,880
Master.

471
00:20:28,000 --> 00:20:29,160
On such a happy day,

472
00:20:29,280 --> 00:20:30,160
make a wish!

473
00:20:30,320 --> 00:20:31,480
I know.

474
00:20:31,640 --> 00:20:32,720
The director's wish

475
00:20:32,720 --> 00:20:34,360
is to top the Imperial Court Exam!

476
00:20:34,360 --> 00:20:35,360
I changed my mind.

477
00:20:36,040 --> 00:20:36,680
I want us

478
00:20:37,600 --> 00:20:39,720
to top the Imperial Court Exam together.

479
00:20:39,720 --> 00:20:40,400
Okay!

480
00:20:42,050 --> 00:20:45,610
[Top the Imperial Court Exam together]

481
00:20:45,640 --> 00:20:47,860
[and become masters]

482
00:20:47,880 --> 00:20:51,570
[Master, be healthy and happy]

483
00:20:51,590 --> 00:20:55,690
[Beat your troubles away]

484
00:21:00,580 --> 00:21:02,670
[Tianhai Family Dungeon]

485
00:21:05,000 --> 00:21:06,720
Chen Changsheng!

486
00:21:06,840 --> 00:21:08,120
Because of you,

487
00:21:08,440 --> 00:21:10,480
I ended up like this.

488
00:21:10,600 --> 00:21:12,080
I want you to die!

489
00:21:15,920 --> 00:21:19,000
Today, I'll start with you.

490
00:21:19,280 --> 00:21:23,410
Tomorrow, I'll flay alive
those bastards
of the State Religious Academy!

491
00:21:26,720 --> 00:21:27,360
Brother!

492
00:21:31,010 --> 00:21:32,940
Weren't you at the northern front?

493
00:21:33,650 --> 00:21:34,910
Why are you back?

494
00:21:35,920 --> 00:21:36,800
Ya'er.

495
00:21:37,360 --> 00:21:39,120
Since childhood, I told you

496
00:21:40,240 --> 00:21:41,480
the Tianhai name

497
00:21:41,640 --> 00:21:43,570
must not be insulted by outsiders.

498
00:21:46,840 --> 00:21:49,880
One Bai Luoheng left you helpless?

499
00:21:53,040 --> 00:21:54,100
You useless thing.

500
00:21:54,200 --> 00:21:55,720
Stay here

501
00:21:55,880 --> 00:21:57,020
and rot.

502
00:22:01,880 --> 00:22:02,800
General!

503
00:22:03,280 --> 00:22:04,480
Attention, troops.

504
00:22:05,760 --> 00:22:08,200
Eliminate the State Religious Academy
at once.

505
00:22:08,200 --> 00:22:11,160
Chen Changsheng.

506
00:22:12,170 --> 00:22:15,930
[To be continued]

507
00:22:17,910 --> 00:22:19,500
Follow on Way of Choices animation.

508
00:22:19,500 --> 00:22:20,880
Light up your Destiny Star.

509
00:22:20,880 --> 00:22:22,740
We hope you all follow your heart.

510
00:22:25,000 --> 00:22:26,040
The Li Palace took Princess Luo away

511
00:22:25,090 --> 00:22:28,630
[In the next episode]

512
00:22:26,320 --> 00:22:27,840
in the early morning.

513
00:22:28,200 --> 00:22:29,200
In my opinion,

514
00:22:29,300 --> 00:22:31,350
it's likely one of Tianhai's dirty tricks.

515
00:22:31,350 --> 00:22:33,100
Those who offend the Tianhai family

516
00:22:33,100 --> 00:22:34,810
must die.

517
00:22:34,810 --> 00:22:35,900
Enough nonsense!

518
00:22:36,840 --> 00:22:38,570
Are you sure you want to do this?

519
00:22:39,240 --> 00:22:41,640
This is the only way
to break the formation.

520
00:22:41,840 --> 00:22:42,520
Trust me!

